| ego  | traj_preds  | 3.97e-3 | 0.9999854 ✅ |
| ego  | occ_logits  | 6.13e-4 | 0.9999966 ✅ |
| ego  | sdc_traj    | 3.33e-4 | 1.0000000 ✅ |

